{"type": "article", "id": 13653, "title": "「 夏末单车」之木质车篮", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-18T08:03:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606153321pZ9WRNDa6InY1fMq.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>来自纽约的两位设计师 Faris Elmasu 和 David Haddad 推出的这款篮子可以被固定在自行车上，它们采用木质材料，上面设计了四条两两交叉的固定带，篮子虽浅，但带子可以保证东西不会落下来。更重要的是，这样浅浅的设计和可以自由搭配的五颜六色的带子，让整个篮子看起来比普通的自行车篮子美丽了许多。</span><a href=\"http://bentbasket.com/products/bent-basket\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a><span>可以购买。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261413453WovjSf0JVsX9Gt2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141346spM31tHgcNFVIXqy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141347pfrkHolsMaz2bLte.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141348urSNU5vXxnwTaPY7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141348ZG3948YItKho2TwA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141349wvjAgkDYV345rGzf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141350KtlpaWcbrG2ksZ7x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<br>\n\n\n\n"}